## 🎨 Design System

### **Color Palette:**
- **Primary:** #1f2937 (Gray-800) - Headers and important text
- **Secondary:** #6b7280 (Gray-500) - Body text and descriptions
- **Accent:** #3b82f6 (Blue-500) - Links and interactive elements
- **Success:** #10b981 (Emerald-500) - Positive indicators
- **Warning:** #f59e0b (Amber-500) - Caution indicators
- **Error:** #ef4444 (Red-500) - Error states
- **Background:** #f9fafb (Gray-50) - Main background
- **Card Background:** #ffffff (White) - Card backgrounds

### **Typography:**
- **Headings:** Inter, 600 weight, 1.2 line height
- **Body:** Inter, 400 weight, 1.5 line height
- **Captions:** Inter, 400 weight, 1.4 line height
- **Code:** JetBrains Mono, 400 weight, 1.4 line height

### **Spacing:**
- **Base Unit:** 8px
- **Small:** 4px (0.5rem)
- **Medium:** 8px (1rem)
- **Large:** 16px (2rem)
- **Extra Large:** 24px (3rem)

### **Border Radius:**
- **Small:** 4px
- **Medium:** 8px
- **Large:** 12px
- **Extra Large:** 16px

